This section constitutes the Software Integration Test Report as required by
EN 50716:2023, Clause 7.6 and Table A.1 (document 21). It records the results
of executing the SW integration test cases defined in the SW Integration Test
Specification (03_architecture_design.sdoc, SAD-070 / SWIT-xxx series) against
the source code baseline identified in 05_component_impl_test.sdoc (CI-010).
<<<

