[REQUIREMENT]
UID: INT-071
STATUS: Draft
TITLE: Verification records and verdict
STATEMENT: >>>
The Software Integration Verification Report shall include:

  - Date and revision of the SW Integration Test Report, HW-SW Integration
    Test Report, and source code baseline reviewed.
  - Name, role, and independence evidence of the verifier (per SP-021).
  - Checklist results: each item marked Pass / Fail / N/A with observations.
  - Confirmation of timing results: all performance budgets met (INT-050, INT-051).
  - Confirmation of coverage: all integration interfaces covered (INT-020).
  - List of findings: unique identifier, description, severity, and status.
  - Action items raised, with reference to the action item register.
  - Resolution evidence for all Critical and Major findings.
  - Overall verdict: Approved / Approved with conditions / Not approved.

The integration test reports shall not be released and software validation
(EN 50716:2023, Clause 7.7) shall not commence until an Approved verdict
is recorded.

